OL,5, The FBI and other US government        
OL,6, agencies failed "at a fundamental      
OL,7, level" to assess the potential for     
OL,8, violence ahead of the Capitol riot on 6
OL,9, January 2021, a new report claims.     
OL,11,FDemocrats on a Senate panel found the  
OL,12,FFBI and the Department of Homeland     
OL,13,FSecurity (DHS) "downplayed" the risks  
OL,14,Fand so did not properly prepare.       
OL,16,FThe 105-page report, titled Planned in 
OL,17,FPlain Sight, was released on Tuesday.  
OL,19,FIt criticises officials for misjudging 
OL,20,Fand reacting slowly to tip-offs.       
